    "body": "Problem:\r\n`api.nvim_buf_del_mark` already emits a `MarkSet` event with `col` and `line` set to 0. However, `:delmarks` currently emits no events.\r\n\r\nSolution:\r\nChange `:delmarks` to emit the same `col==line==0` event.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nthis is a backport of https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/39156 to release-0.12 - see that PR for details!\r\n\r\nthe only conflict was news.txt - I can't seem to find a backport PR with a change to news.txt that I can copy the style of, so I'm not sure if it should go into news.txt or news-0.12.txt (I guess news-0.12.txt is nonexistent on the release-0.12 branch?), or what\r\n\r\nfyi @justinmk",
    "closed_at": "2026-04-19T12:20:56Z",
    "comment_data": [],
    "comment_regular_data": [
