            "body": "> I guess news-0.12.txt is nonexistent on the release-0.12 branch?\r\n\r\nyes, so just add it to the news.txt (as you did here 👍 )\r\n\r\nthis is something we need to improve... historically we haven't usually backported \"features\" to the release branches so it was less of a problem.",
